#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_clearmotd.html.heex:11
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Clears the server MOTD that is normally displayed to users when they connect. After clearing, the MOTD section is simply skipped during connection. You can set a new MOTD at any time with"
