#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/cmd_query.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Creates or switches to a PM conversation tab with the specified user. No message is sent — it simply opens the window so you can start typing. If you already have a PM tab open with that user, it switches to it. If you want to open the tab"
